Sao Martinho May Invest $950 Million in Sugar Output, Valor Says

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-06-29T13:20:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-29/sao-martinho-may-invest-950-million-in-sugar-output-valor-says.html
Sao Martinho SA (SMTO3)  may invest as much
as 1.5 billion reais ($950 million) to expand sugar and ethanol
production in  Brazil  in coming years,  Valor Economico  reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Fabio Venturelli.  Sao Martinho may also consider acquisitions, Venturelli
told the Sao Paulo-based newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in Sao Paulo at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 